---
title: Pork in Creamy Mushroom Sauce with fluffy rice and softened leeks
description: There are many reasons this creamy mushroom pork recipe makes the perfect weeknight meal. It's super speedy to make and it's also made up of those favourite flavours the family is sure to love—with a helping of veg thrown in for good measure.
